        "children": [
          "Basics"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-3"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Watch panels light up, then repeat the pattern. Each round adds one step. Miss too many and it's game over!"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-text"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-4"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Browser Controls"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-5"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Click — Select panel | 1-9 — Quick select"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-key"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-6"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Q/W — Use power-ups | ESC — Pause | R — Rematch"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-key"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-7"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "VR Controls"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-8"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Trigger — Select | B — Pause | A — Power-up"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-key"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-9"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Laser pointer — Menu navigation"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-key"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-10"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "8 Game Modes"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-11"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Classic: Standard. Speed: Gets faster. Reverse: Repeat backwards. Rush: 60s time limit. Zen: Infinite lives. Daily: Same for everyone. Survival: One mistake. Marathon: Level 50 goal."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-text"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-12"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Power-Ups"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-13"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Replay: See sequence again. Slow-Mo: Half speed for 2 rounds. Shield: Block one mistake. Hint: Flash the next panel."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-text"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-14"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Earned at level milestones (3, 5, 10, 15...)."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-tip"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-15"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Scoring Tips"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-16"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Build combos — every 5 correct hits increases your multiplier."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-tip"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-17"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Complete rounds quickly for bonus points."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-tip"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-18"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Higher difficulty = bigger XP rewards."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-tip"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-19"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Daily streaks award bonus XP!"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-tip"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-20"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Strategy"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-21"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Start with Quad (4 panels) to learn the rhythm."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-tip"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-22"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Use panel shapes and positions, not just colors."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-tip"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-23"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Save Shield for deep sequences (level 15+)."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-tip"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-24"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Zen mode is great for practice."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-tip"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-25"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Challenges"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-26"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Generate a 6-character code and share it. Anyone with the code plays the exact same sequence — compete for the best score!"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-text"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-27"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "XP and Unlocks"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "class": "help-section"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-28"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "span",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Earn XP every game. Level up to unlock new panel skins and arena themes. 50 levels from Newbie to NEON GOD."
